Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汝乃冒险者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够潜过名为『危险』之瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,探求位于其深处的 传说真相之人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是 就来将吾寻得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接连发生离奇的船难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人们谣传此为自古便栖息于 海底的怪兽所为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各国首脑则认为此为 新武器之攻击而彼此责难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,紧张的气氛不断升温
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在此同时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自工业革命后 工业与科学迅速发展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各强国为了争夺亚洲 非洲殖民地而彼此对立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,军事冲突一再上演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,19世纪末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有志之士们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都笼罩在一触即发的 世界大战阴影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:27.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:33.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:45.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:51.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:59.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:06.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:15.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:20.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:25.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:31.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:37.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴黎…巴黎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是艾菲尔铁塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:29.30,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#01 艾菲尔铁塔的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好壮观喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是巴黎万国博览会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还需要再等一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要推挤 请不要推挤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 光这样还是飞不上天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 驱动系统显得太累赘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总觉得自己好像是来看人 而不是来看发明的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在宣布第一届国际飞行比赛 正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这项竞赛内容为 飞行距离愈远者获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,优胜者可获得2万法郎奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 我来晚了\N是吗 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 1号机快要掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你看那家伙如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那样的机翼 根本撑不住引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风力2啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然是顺风 但能飞个8公尺就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纪录为8公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然\N果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来是2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特地越过多佛海峡 从英国远道而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿克莱特爵爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活该 笨贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈 我们是几号？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我抽到102号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那要等到傍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然早了点 先把机体从船上卸下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你坐船过来时有没有晕船啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有 一路都很舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在船上完成这么多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 真抱歉 都怪我不能搭船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一点都不在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一说到船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说美国派出了新战舰 要去对付海底的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以为你爸报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不确定他已经过世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊…说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,22号机 皮耶号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,优胜呼声很高喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照这情况来看 优胜是我们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们应该会获得 压倒性的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下子2万法郎的奖金 也是我们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天起可以肆无忌惮地 尽情发明了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下我老婆可没话说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要先好好玩遍巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你一心想找到你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你也该找个女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人生只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开心享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 把那边的扳手拿给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈 我先离开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,2万法郎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傍晚我一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,2万法郎耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,错不了 就是那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个 可千万别让她给逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看她的目的地应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾菲尔铁塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,法国 西班牙 意大利 埃及 非洲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 我到底来自哪个国家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会跟你一样都是非洲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算问你你也不会知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是能飞的话 或许就能去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是能带你飞上天的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的飞得起来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是为了参加那场飞行大赛 而从勒阿弗尔来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 我来猜猜看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是印度对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思 我并不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 你终于开口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还在担心跟你语言会不通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 我并不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也觉得我的肤色很罕见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就难说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有啦 我想说难得来巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想跟你交个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好奇怪的猫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,表情别那么阴沉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人生只有一次 开心享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开心享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？ 好厉害的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当众谈情说爱 好歹也要有点分寸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从刚才一直看着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没完没了 没完没了…\N大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别迁怒到小孩子身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对对 还是快点进入正题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖把你胸前的 玻璃坠子交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了寻找拥有这东西的你 我们可是跑遍了整个欧洲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然…\N不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对小孩子这样做 实在太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跳起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快追！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别跑！\N别跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然让她给跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 我晓得那女孩会去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看她的身手加上那只怪猫 当然就是那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改变计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁着还没有人来 我们快下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轻盈的身手加上怪猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了 是马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔 这个女孩的表演何时开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 原来她平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,表演的时间到了 快换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,团长 今天我不想上台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总觉得会发生什么不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天你有吃早餐对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就该付出同等的劳力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位来宾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在就来介绍她出场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,丛林舞姬 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来她叫娜蒂亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以摆出一副 凶神恶煞的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次可要合法地 与对方沟通喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 使用伪币算合法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太多话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有点事想跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多多麦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,薛提 奈费特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请各位给予热烈的掌声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以上是娜蒂亚公主的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bonjour, Mademoiselle. (小姐您好)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了 她不是你的姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我叫葛兰迪丝·格兰帕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直在找你 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟姐姐一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女孩子还是送花好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这样挣扎个不停 吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从现在起 我就是你的监护人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还付了钱 谢谢人家对你至今的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给她三分颜色 她倒开起染坊来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不白费唇舌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我抓回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命\N遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才那3个人要抓你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就坐这个一起逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以靠自己摆脱他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别叫我名字 好像我们很熟似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经不是马戏团演员了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别那么逞强嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些家伙 为什么要抢这颗石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这东西那么珍贵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不想说就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用跑的是追不上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 是铁制的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是谁发明的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不想尝苦头的话就过来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要好好让你们明白 瞧不起大人会有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种玩具怎么可能逃得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要动手了 大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 放手去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森\N我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们别这样啦 很危险耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小鬼 不可以妨碍大人办事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就去反省一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁着还没有人来碍事 快用飞行模式开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真危险 我还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,缠人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么处理？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随他去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正『蔚蓝之水』 已经在我们手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Goodbye！ Adios！ (再见)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见\N再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等你好久了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上就能飞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能再快一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样已经是最快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还不如在地上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轮到99号机 日之本号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然有人突然插队？\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,往上飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直接飞越多佛海峡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再会了 心爱的花都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让开 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你没事吧？\N我挣脱不开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是用纸做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点制住这只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是狮子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 我可不想年纪轻轻 就坠机死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心 下面是塞纳河
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那两个孩子还蛮有本事的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我绝对不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会放弃蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走水路他们就追不上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们就开这艘船逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会不会冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会 你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？我没说过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好过份喔 强 我叫强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你接下来有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要回马戏团吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你的家人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊 那就跟我一样啰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.57,0:22:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就到勒阿弗尔来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:22:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我姑丈家也在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈跟姑姑都是很热心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定会愿意帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 强 是特别奖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 因为是临时奖项 所以没有奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要好好干喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:53.93,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:24:01.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:07.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:11.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:20.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:30.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.60,0:24:39.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.31,0:24:43.54,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.61,0:24:48.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:57.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.43,0:25:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 这就是我的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.30,0:25:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些全都是你做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.44,0:25:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会开我发明的飞机 送你回故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.78,0:25:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.51,0:25:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖交出蔚蓝之水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好烦人的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.78,0:25:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是姐姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『小小逃亡者』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.25,0:25:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
